{"tid":2314384,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"做足5年淡倉 對沖基金終向Tesla認輸","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T00:54:53.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc70bdad4535d9686a66605b8fd9d09e58ba8dc","tid":2314384,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"著名對沖基金 Kynikos Associates 終於遇上對手，該公司在 5 年前曾因對電動車生產商 Tesla（NASDAQ 上市編號：TSLA）的股票「做淡倉」 而大賺，但時至今日終於要認低威。原因是在頭 4 年 Tesla 的股價沒有大幅波動，但踏入 2020 年後股價卻急升超過 5 倍，結果成為 Kynikos 成立 35 年來最困難的 1 年。<br />\n<br />\n曾做淡倉大賺 認為 Tesla 盈利數字有水份<br />\nKynikos 創辦人 Jim Chanos 已著手減少 Tesla 相關的淡倉，但他接受訪問時表示依然相信後者的盈利數字，是以稅務手段達成絕不實際，相信問題會隨時間過去而暴露出來。由於 Tesla 早前年報已實現業務盈利，因此已被納入成為標普 500 指數成分股，而受到大小基金不問價追貨。"},{"pid":"1c6ce5217f6e1053ef5021404412bc1cf44a70c4","tid":2314384,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"即係到咗高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50e430d05ef17939961f21eaabdcd97caa7e0cf","tid":2314384,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"我接力"},{"pid":"19a4d6b2e34e9e793c3196098c3a986fe35634c0","tid":2314384,"uid":33618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"淡友一認輸就跌，好鬼邪"},{"pid":"68962704d416b866483223c9ad949edf5e95bd8b","tid":2314384,"uid":110398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"Jump得"},{"pid":"c158957da2e4c2376742112e425a2e2908486e65","tid":2314384,"uid":364041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"抵死 同神作對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c9582c22c981a81913f14f8f0cbb000f083bdf","tid":2314384,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"5年..."},{"pid":"72ccba9df6f159031ae10d8374ee327d0de96137","tid":2314384,"uid":180251,"like"